- Pleasure.
- Business.

15
00:01:20,240 --> 00:01:21,958
How long will you be staying?

16
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,998
Could I see your return ticket?

17
00:01:25,080 --> 00:01:28,470
- What's the purpose of your visit?
- Business or pleasure?

18
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:31,438
Enjoy your stay. Next.

19
00:01:31,520 --> 00:01:35,035
<i>[Tannoy] Please have your passports,
immigration forms, I-94,</i>

20
00:01:35,120 --> 00:01:38,715
<i>and customs declarations
