Gupta, will you relax?
Just watch the door.

1049
01:15:46,560 --> 01:15:49,438
You go in jail. Not me.

1050
01:15:49,520 --> 01:15:51,351
For... You know what? Forget it.

1051
01:15:51,440 --> 01:15:53,112
- Keep looking.
- Warren, right?

1052
01:15:53,200 --> 01:15:54,872
- Yes. Yes.
- Warren.

1053
01:15:54,960 --> 01:15:56,552
Amelia Jane Warren?

1054
