Please. Please. Please. Please.

1121
01:21:20,000 --> 01:21:24,357
Sorry. So, tonight we have
cannellonis or chicken.

1122
01:21:24,440 --> 01:21:27,113
- Cannelloni, please.
- Cannelloni.

1123
01:21:27,200 --> 01:21:29,077
- Sorry.
- Thank you.

1124
01:21:29,160 --> 01:21:30,957
For you, sir?

1125
01:21:31,040 --> 01:21:34,032
- Same.
- That's a great, great choice.

1126
01:21:34,120 --> 01:21:36,031
I'll be back.

1127
01:21:49,520 --> 01:21:52,876
Let me see. Enjoy.

1128
01:21:54,280 --> 01:21:57,158
Did you know the croissant
was invented in Romania?

1129
01:21:57,240 --> 01:21:59,800
- Tell me.
- OK.

1130
01:21:59,880 --> 01:22:03,429
It's 1742
and the Turks invade Bucharest,

1131
01:22:03,520 --> 01:22:06,512
making a surprise attack
under the cover of night.

1132
01:22:06,600 --> 01:22:09,068
<i>- But the town bakers...
- [pager beeps]</i>

1133
01:22:10,880 --> 01:22:12,791
Sorry.

1134
01:22:22,600 --> 01:22:24,511
[Clattering]

1135
01:22:28,920 --> 01:22:31,195
So, the bakers?

1136
01:22:31,280 --> 01:22:35,637
- No, never mind. It's a dumb story.
- No, please.

1137
01:22:35,720 --> 01:22:36,994
I'm sorry, Viktor.

1138
01:22:37,080 --> 01:22:40,834
Nobody really cares
where the croissant was invented.

1139
01:22:40,920 --> 01:22:44,356
I'll bet the Romanians themselves
don't give a shit.

1140
01:22:44,440 --> 01:22:45,668
I care.

1141
01:22:45,760 --> 01:22:48,513
Is histories. Is truth.

1142
01:22:49,560 --> 01:22:52,120
- I'm 39 years old.
- No.

