1153
01:23:24,440 --> 01:23:25,953
<i>[Pager beeps]</i>

1154
01:23:27,720 --> 01:23:30,871
You can switch off pager.

1155
01:23:32,080 --> 01:23:33,513
I wish I could.

1156
01:23:33,600 --> 01:23:37,036
I've been waiting for a phone call
for seven years.

1157
01:23:37,120 --> 01:23:41,318
I know it's coming, Viktor.
That's why I can't break it off.

1158
01:23:42,040 --> 01:23:46,591
That's why I live out of hotels and have
my little suitcase packed, ready to go,

1159
01:23:46,680 --> 01:23:49,069
just in case
he wants to meet me for the weekend.

1160
01:23:50,200 --> 01:23:52,111
Yeah.

1161
01:23:52,680 --> 01:23:54,591
I've been waiting my whole life.

1162
01:23:57,800 --> 01:24:01,759
<i>- Just don't know what the hell for.
- [Pager vibrates]</i>

1163
01:24:03,880 --> 01:24:05,836
I'm so sorry.

1164
01:24:23,120 --> 01:24:25,429
[Viktor] I live here.

1165
01:24:25,520 --> 01:24:27,556
- What?
- I live here, in terminal.

1166
01:24:27,640 --> 01:24:29,551
Gate 67.

1167
01:24:30,360 --> 01:24:33,352
- You live at the airport?
- Yes. Day and night.

1168
01:24:33,440 --> 01:24:36,910
This home, like you.
They tell me to wait.

1169
01:24:37,000 --> 01:24:38,718
So I wait.

1170
01:24:38,800 --> 01:24:41,519
All frequent fliers
feel the same way you do, Viktor.

1171
01:24:41,600 --> 01:24:43,716
Everybody's waiting. Everybody.

1172
01:24:43,800 --> 01:24:48,316
- For a flight, for a meeting...
- I don't wait for flight or meeting.

1173
01:24:48,400 --> 01:24:50,789
<i>- Then what are you waiting for?
- [Pager beeps]</i>

1174
01:24:53,880 --> 01:24:56,758
Is OK. I understand.

1175
01:25:00,080 --> 01:25:01,991
I have an idea.

1176
01:25:03,160 --> 01:25:05,754
- Come here.
- What you do?

1177
01:25:07,960 --> 01:25:09,188
You sure?

1178
01:25:09,280 --> 01:25:11,714
More than anything, I'm sure of this.

1179
01:25:11,800 --> 01:25:13,711
Ready?

1180
01:25:18,560 --> 01:25:20,471
[Both laugh]

1181
01:25:28,120 --> 01:25:31,078
[Viktor] So, when do you come back?

1182
01:25:31,160 --> 01:25:34,311
